content.text: Paldean Fates celebrates the brilliance and destiny of Pokémon from across the Paldea region, where every encounter shines with possibility. Discover stunning Shiny Pokémon, dazzling full-art designs, and abilities that embody the spirit of adventure and discovery. With Radiant mechanics and shimmering new variants, this expansion lets you forge your own path, defy the odds, and shape your story in a world illuminated by fate. Your journey begins anew—embrace your shining destiny in Paldean Fates.
